Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabaul Air Corps (Episode 15)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,50 aircraft passed over the First Observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,New formations of 30 planes, then the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be over 100 aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, the number is increasing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our planes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Already less than half.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the withdrawal from Guadalcanal Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabaul Base on New Britain Island has been on the frontlines, protecting the southern resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in the summer of 1943,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:03:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the sea and air superiority around Rabaul had already been transferred from the Japanese army to the US army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The main target of the US military is to block the Japanese supply line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, to destroy supply ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to their overwhelming quantity, the US military, conducting counter-offensive operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,launched air raids on Rabaul, the main point of the Japanese military's southern base, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The 26th Air Squadron Command
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Combined Fleet Command still stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, it seems that they are not thinking about reinforcements for Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rabaul Air Corps should do its best as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's a terrible word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the flight captain's reconnaissance aircraft report hundreds of planes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,have gathered at the airfield centered on Guadalcanal Island in New Guinea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and their attack power has been strengthened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to leave them as is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE {Possibly part of previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aviation staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return to headquarters on Truck Island now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to meet with the Commander-in-Chief of the Allied Fleet Koga in person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and express my sense of urgency at the situation at Rabaul base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be too late after the staff returns to Truck Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy MTFs and convoys frequently haunt the coast of Bougainville and the Coral Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Headquarters. Headquarters. This is the 305th Squadron. I discovered the enemy task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two aircraft carriers, two cruisers, and six destroyers are moving east-northeast in a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad, looking at recent air raids and movement of enemy ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemy is now planning to land on Bougainville or New Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's strike them. If we don't hit them now, it will be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a task force including the southern two aircraft carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Headquarters. Headquarters. I've just discovered another target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the pattern of the convoy closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yabe. come back. Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the enemy intends to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bougainville or New Britain has been decided. If this fleet is left as it is, we will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I need an airplane. Do the people in the mainland know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they think there are hundreds or thousands of planes left in Rabaul?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, what does the Combined Fleet Say to our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategy discussions are underway. Engage in the given operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was blurred, then Rabaul would also be a repeat of Guadalcanal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Headquarters. Headquarters. Another convoys of about 20 enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Several Grummans are attacking from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yabe, are you okay? Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Communication has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot stand it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sasagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me fly. I will save Yabe alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Do not get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, I am not afraid to die. I am ready to die at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasagawa, I understand your feelings well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We are friends who vowed to be together when we die, but the military has must have discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No reckless action is allowed until there is a sortie order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sasagawa, it's easy to die, but don't die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yabe knew he would never return, but he dived into the enemy anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We will cherish a little more life to reward his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, we can die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Sasagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yonezawa, a member of the press team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Combined Fleet on Truck Island is unlikely to move to Rabaul’s request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is certain that the enemy's target is Guadalcanal and then Bougainville or New Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the great men willing to abandon the base at Rabaul?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a fighter. The strategy is decided beyond our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but a strategy that ignores the intention of this front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Battle of Midway, the Combined Fleet has become stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Midway was supposed to be a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the reality of Rabaul is faithfully conveyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the duty of the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, please tell the people on the mainland to send as many planes as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be that the Rabaul Air Corps was sung in songs and boasted of its invincibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilots longed for this Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am the maintenance manager Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This was shot in a daytime air raid, but if I replace the engine, it could be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one aircraft is precious at this base now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By tomorrow morning, we will have a great air battle and we need the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, at the Combined Fleet Command on Truck Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A fleet of two aircraft carriers, three cruisers, four destroyers, and 10 cargo ships are moving north.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, Rabaul’s patrol aircraft found another fleet off the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? So how many fleets are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They discovered an enemy fleet of one aircraft carrier, two cruisers, and five cargo ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, next is Bougainville or New Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, return the planes and ships on Truck Island to Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in time if we act now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabaul’s soldiers are waiting for the Chief's decision. Morale is also strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to bring together all the strength of the navy and hit the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I also agree with the opinion of the aviation staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit enemies from the sea in the sea. This is the ironclad rule of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, Rabaul makes increasing requests every day. Turn your aviation planes and fleets over to Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's aim is Bougainville or New Britain, there is no doubt now. After they land, we will regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. It may be a chance to relieve the black mark of Midway and Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the morale of the soldiers is high. Let's beat the arrogant and rude enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, call Lieutenant General Ozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander-in-Chief of the Allied Fleet Koga made a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in response to the the request of the front-line base: Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Fleet under the command of Vice Admiral Ozawa and all of his planes were dispatched to Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Operational decisions require agility and courage. In that sense, this decision slows the American side slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Early in the morning of the day when the Ozawa fleet arrived in Rabaul, 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the U.S. military fleet of 18 transport ships and nine escort ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which had been hidden due to bad weather on the previous day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly landed on Cape Torokina on the west coast of Bougainville Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was November 1st, 1943.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I brought in reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE {Not even sure you want to translate this, but he says something}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,70 Zuikaku attack aircraft of the Ozawa fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,70 Chokaku Zero aircraft,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and 30 Zuiho carrier-capable aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, a total of 180 aircraft should be here by the 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy to see this much reinforcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. It's a pity that we didn't allow the enemy to land in Torokina one day earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Have you been transferred to Rabaul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be fine and above all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pray for continued luck in the fortunes of war and make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You wonder why I didn't order the Ozawa fleet to be dispatched before the enemy invaded Torokina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors that you are a good pilot, but I'm glad to have such a nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These times are terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you aspire to be a lawyer, you look like a soldier now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years will it take to become a full-fledged airplane pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE {May just be part of the last line}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It will take at least five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to waste the excellent pilots who take five years to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, air power will be the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this war will end only in Rabaul?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy, who is proud of their numerical quantity are now trying to make a big counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In such a case, it may be necessary to retreat and rebuild the formation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than fighting the enemy with all one's might.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are a relative, I just complained.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. even though you used to call me uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to meet you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Koga. You volunteered for such an assignment, what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabaul isn't as easy as the mainland. Like the song now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is encouraging to know that the captain of the 305th is Senior Kamijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. 30 degrees forward to the right, enemy plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter the clouds in front of you and make a reverse drop. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Rabaul air corps
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our silvery wings come together at the Southern Front
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The unshaken defense of our Sea Eagles
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At the enemy's frontline of human bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honor is with us. We are the Rabaul Naval Air Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rabaul Air Corps made a fearless attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The result of the battle was announced spectacularly by the Imperial Headquarters at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Rabaul’s air power was gradually exhausted in the face of the unending amount of American troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Air combat was still going on on Bougainville Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On November 13th, 1943, an unbelievable situation occurred in the Rabaul Air Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The headquarters of the Ozawa Third Fleet, who came with reinforcements from Truck Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly started pulling back toward Truck Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be just us in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with all the aircraft that can sortie at Rabaul Base, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,an order has been issued to attack and destroy enemy task forces moving north on the sea west of Bougainville Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing new to do in the sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just pray for you a good fight and your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, please take me too. I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You are injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you said we would die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait at the Sanzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come after healing that arm as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, this may be your last chance to see Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kamijo. My uncle asked me if I thought Rabaul alone would end the next war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Koga. You care about the Ozawa fleet pulling out of Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting it. In the heart of your uncle, Commander-in-Chief of the Allied Fleet. {I think "I was expecting it" is from another speaker, but HA does not use a > here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is more important for a master to fall back than to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for those of us who pulled the Ozawa fleet out of Truck Island and made your uncle's cool mind go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all listening? Let's end the battle only for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But never hurry to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Live as much as you can and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the enemy's mobile unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Upper right sky, enemy planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am engaged with the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about subsequent communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going home alive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kamijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the soul of Rabaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On February 1st, 1944, the US military jumped and landed on the Marshall Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On February 17th, the MTF attacked Drag Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after air raids on Tinian and Saipan, Rabaul was completely isolated behind the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of this hill-rolling momentum, is any decision useless or helpless?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It may just be known only to heaven.
